'''Orko SkyMine Asteroid Processing Corporation''' was a fake corporation set up by [[Durga Besadii Tai|Durga the Hutt]]. It was made to hide a huge amount of credits; the company was supposed to be a commercial venture to exploit the riches of the [[Hoth asteroid field/Legends|Hoth asteroid field]], but in fact the money was being diverted to the top secret [[Darksaber (superweapon)|''Darksaber'']] Project.

